### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================
### RECIPE ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get All Recipes (with pagination)
GET {{apiUrl}}/recipes?page=1&limit=12

### Get All Recipes with Filters
GET {{apiUrl}}/recipes?difficulty=easy&cuisine=italian&maxTime=30

### Get Recipe by ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/recipes/recipe-001

### Get Available Cuisines
GET {{apiUrl}}/recipes/cuisines

### Get Dietary Options
GET {{apiUrl}}/recipes/dietary

### Search Recipes by Ingredients
POST {{apiUrl}}/recipes/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredients": ["chicken", "tomato", "garlic", "onion"],
  "dietary": "gluten-free",
  "maxTime": 45,
  "difficulty": "easy"
}

### Intelligent Recipe Matching
POST {{apiUrl}}/recipes/match
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredients": ["pasta", "cheese", "eggs", "bacon"],
  "preferences": {
    "dietary": "",
    "maxTime": 30,
    "difficulty": "medium"
  }
}

### Get Ingredient Substitutions
POST {{apiUrl}}/recipes/substitute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredient": "butter"
}

### Analyze Image (Base64)
POST {{apiUrl}}/recipes/analyze-image
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRg..."
}

### ============================================
### USER ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Toggle Favorite Recipe
POST {{apiUrl}}/user/favorites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipeId": "recipe-001",
  "userId": "test-user-123"
}

### Get User Favorites
GET {{apiUrl}}/user/favorites?userId=test-user-123

### Rate Recipe
POST {{apiUrl}}/user/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipeId": "recipe-001",
  "rating": 5,
  "userId": "test-user-123"
}

### Get Recommendations
GET {{apiUrl}}/user/recommendations?userId=test-user-123&limit=10

### ============================================
### ERROR TESTING
### ============================================

### Invalid Recipe ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/recipes/invalid-id

### Search without Ingredients
POST {{apiUrl}}/recipes/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredients": []
}


### Search without Ingredients
POST {{apiUrl}}/recipes/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredients": ["chicken", "tomato", "garlic"]
}

### Invalid Rating
POST {{apiUrl}}/user/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipeId": "recipe-001",
  "rating": 5
}